@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ptxulr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.exp((v2 + wp.abs(v1 + 0.71)))
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = 0.95
    v0 = 0.97
    v0 = wp.sin(0.20)
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.abs(v0 + 0.39) + v2))
    data[tid] = v0
